# ── Secrets ──
# Catches local dev env, bridge server .env, bot daemon .env, etc.
# Bridge server uses JWT_SECRET / ADMIN_TOKEN / ENCRYPTION_KEY_HEX —
# a leaked .env to git history = compromised auth + decryptable token store.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.template
